high_descs: Turn around and go to the left side of the white table
Grab an apple off of the table
Turn right and go to the microwave
Heat the apple in the microwave and then take it out
Move slightly to the left and look down at the sink
Put the apple in the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting a hot apple in the sink

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the wall, turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the apple closest to the coffee machine on the white table.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a left and walk towards the fridge, turn right and walk up to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and heat it up for a couple seconds then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the heated apple in the rightmost sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room and turn right at the table.
Pick up the apple on the table.
Go around the table and turn right to the microwave.
Microwave the apple and take it out of the microwave.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple in the sink.
